Just like with the exam, you're expected to arrive <u>45 minutes prior</u> to the inspection. There will be an Assistant Floor Manager (AFM'er) on location who will tend to the technical aspect of the inspection, while you're expected to take care of the content. The inspection is protected with a password, which the AFM'er will share with the students when you're ready to start the inspection. Please refer to <a href="https://canvas.uva.nl/courses/45162/pages/tools-ans-inspection">this page</a> for more information regarding inspections.
